videos.description: Bashir Ahmed misses his layup but Tariq Owens slams the ball in on the rebound.
videos.headline: Red Storm's Owens with putback dunk

videos.description: Angel Delgado kicks it out to Khadeen Carrington on the wing, who drains an easy 3-pointer.
videos.headline: Seton Hall's Carrington swishes easy 3

videos.description: The Red Storm steal the ball from the Pirates and Bashir Ahmed misses the breakaway dunk.
videos.headline: St. John's Ahmed misses dunk

videos.description: Justin Simon lobs the ball perfectly to Tariq Owens who jams the ball in.
videos.headline: St. John's sends in alley-oop dunk

videos.description: Desi Rodriguez sinks a 3-pointer to help Seton Hall complete a 9-0 run.
videos.headline: Pirates go on 9-0 run

videos.description: Myles Powell and Sandro Mamukelashvili work a give-and-go as Powell drains the 3-pointer.
videos.headline: Seton Hall's Powell with give-and-go 3

videos.description: Khadeen Carrington sinks three consecutive 3-pointers, two off of Angel Delgado assists.
videos.headline: Carrington drains three consecutive 3s
